<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
  <head>
    <meta content='text/html; charset=UTF-8' http-equiv='Content-Type' />
  </head>
  <body>
    <h4>Dear User,</h4>
    <p>
      You have successfully placed an order with Lexicon.
      <br/><br/>
      To track your Order please quote the following Order ID:<%= @order.id -%> for future communication.
      <br/><br/>
      Below is your order summary:<br/>
      <% @order.order_items.each do |li| %>
        <%= "#{li.product.name} - #{li.unit_price}, Quantity: #{li.quantity} - Total: #{li.total_price}"%>
        <br/>
      <% end -%>
      <br/>
      Grand Total: <%= @order.total.to_f -%>
      <br/><br/>
    </p>
    <p>Thanks and have a great day!</p>
  </body>
</html>